{"tid":2106924,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"賣衫賣到咁撚串","createTime":"2020-07-13T14:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T23:29:45.000Z","uid":96664,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"91cd7e3b1c8c99e7118202ae0c70f8e091ce1809","tid":2106924,"uid":96664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKfJu8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKfJu8e.jpg&h=8f3c4db2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講錯代購代理都俾佢狂窒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n要特登話自己係代理 唔係代購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時見到佢出story 都好有自信 話咩自己放棄高薪厚職嚟開ig shop <br />\n又狂出story讚自己眼光好好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢份人都好撚囂張下<br />\n有冇人知呢個店主咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做過咩高薪厚職咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2869844a4d9c45995daa3ca98d2b5f36facab500","tid":2106924,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"PTGF同雞，有咩分別？"},{"pid":"c336f630760bac62663cffdc20094bf326210611","tid":2106924,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"係真係打錯字定自己柒咗先<br />\n<br />\n你覺得佢如果係假代理咪起佢底再告佢"},{"pid":"a10c543a85292520bf1b50fd08676637cf14e371","tid":2106924,"uid":96664,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c336f630760bac62663cffdc20094bf326210611","tid":2106924,"uid":168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"係真係打錯字定自己柒咗先<br />\n<br />\n你覺得佢如果係假代理咪起佢底再告佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:16:33.000Z","msg":"冇話佢係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但人講一句佢都要啫住晒咁：你要代購呢我呢道就冇啦請過住 我係代購 好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係想買嘢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad